title: The third Deontay Wilder - Tyson Fury fight lived up to the expectations - Shannon I UNDISPUTED
author: Skip and Shannon: UNDISPUTED
description:
The third fight between Tyson Fury and Deontay Wilder lived up to the hype. Both guys went blow-for-blow in an instant classic that finished with Fury emerging victorious after knocking Wilder to the mat in the 11th round. Skip Bayless and Shannon Sharpe rate the fight on the all-time great scale of 1-10.

#Undisputed #PBC #FuryWilder3
